snippet.textDisplay:
5:42 - 5:46


Wow.

I wish Mac would have realized how many people he had in his corner... how much love and support all of us og diehard fans had for him, and have. He literally helped raise a whole generation of kids, kids that now some have their own kids, and blast his shit in the kitchen making cookies and cleaning dishes. I listen when folding clothes. My kid jams the f out when I throw his songs on. She sat there while my heart broke hearing the news of his passing, as he was a big part of my teen years, my friends teen years, an idol to us. We miss him. Everyday. And will continue to play his music, and carry on his legacy.
